{
  "version": "0.4",
  "title": "XCP Home Part 3 - Checkerboard Layouts",
  "type": "page",
  "content": [
    {
      "id": "checkerboard-1",
      "elType": "section",
      "settings": {
        "_title": "Checkerboard Section 1 - Image Left",
        "layout": "full_width"
      },
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "checker-1-image",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {
            "_column_size": 50,
            "_column_size_mobile": 100,
            "background_image": {
              "url": "[uc_local]assets/images/checkerboard-1.jpg"
            }
          },
          "elements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "checker-1-content",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {
            "_column_size": 50,
            "_column_size_mobile": 100,
            "content_position": "middle"
          },
          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "checker-1-heading",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "heading",
              "settings": {
                "title": "Not Everyone Wants the Polished Version of Themselves",
                "header_size": "h2"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "checker-1-text",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>Your brand isn't like everyone else's. So why should your imagery be?</p><p>You operate in spaces where quality is assumed. The question is whether your visuals reflect the real character behind the brand. Not polished into something safe and forgettable. Not softened for an audience that wouldn't get it anyway.</p><p>Authentic branding photography captures what words can't: the energy, the edge, the unmistakable essence that makes the right people stop and think. That's exactly who I need to work with.</p>"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "checkerboard-2",
      "elType": "section",
      "settings": {
        "_title": "Checkerboard Section 2 - Image Right",
        "layout": "full_width"
      },
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "checker-2-content",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {
            "_column_size": 50,
            "_column_size_mobile": 100,
            "content_position": "middle"
          },
          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "checker-2-heading",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "heading",
              "settings": {
                "title": "Real Moments Land Harder Than Staged Ones",
                "header_size": "h2"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "checker-2-text",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>Your audience doesn't just want pretty pictures. They want to feel something.</p><p>Documentary-style imagery brings depth and authenticity to your brand story. It captures real moments, genuine emotion, and the human side of what you do. This is where connection happens.</p><p>When the right people see themselves reflected in your story, they don't just engage. They recognise you. That's not a metric. That's the person you were trying to reach.</p>"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "checker-2-image",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {
            "_column_size": 50,
            "_column_size_mobile": 100,
            "background_image": {
              "url": "[uc_local]assets/images/checkerboard-2.jpg"
            }
          },
          "elements": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}